'''Nadine Ibrahim''' (wavutse 1993/1994 ) ni umuyobozi wa firime ya Nigeriya.

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Ibrahim yavukiye i Kaduna akurira ari Umuyisilamu. Nyina, Amina J. Mohammed yahoze ari minisitiri w’ibidukikije muri Nijeriya akaba n'Umunyamabanga mukuru wungirije w’umuryango w’abibumbye  . <ref name="okoro">https://guardian.ng/guardian-woman/nadine-ibrahim-i-want-to-tell-stories-that-can-change-the-world/</ref> Igihe yari akiri muto, yashishikajwe no kuvuga inkuru no gukina filime aho kuba amasomo gakondo. <ref name="samanga">https://www.okayafrica.com/nadine-ibrahim-film-nigeria-nollywood/</ref> Yavuye muri Nijeriya yerekeza mu Bwongereza afite imyaka 14 <ref>https://mrsceonaija.com/2018/02/25/lessons-on-breaking-into-the-movie-industry-nadine-ibrahim-films-to-the-world/</ref> yiga itangazamakuru no gutunganya amashusho muri kaminuza ya Gloucestershire . Mubindi bintu, yakoraga imishinga [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|yumuryango w’abibumbye]] na firime za Fictionless. <ref name="okoro" /> Ibrahim yari producer wungirije wa ''Hakkunde'', hafi ya Nigeriya yepfo uhura numuco wamajyaruguru kunshuro yambere. <ref name="future">https://awards.thefutureafrica.com/the-future-awards-africa-prize-for-screen-producer/</ref>

Filime ye ngufi ya documentaire ''Through Her Eyes'' yasohotse muri 2017. Iravuga amateka ya Azeeza, umukobwa wimyaka 12 washimuswe ahinduka umwiyahuzi. Iyi filime yari kimwe cya kabiri kirangiza mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Los Angeles kandi yatowe mu cyiciro cya filime ngufi mu Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime muri Afrika.  Kubitsinda ryitangazamakuru EbonyLife firime na tereviziyo yakoresheje firime avuga inkuru zamoko yo mumajyaruguru ya Nijeriya, nka Hausa, Fulani, Igbira, Igala, Tiv na Gbagyi .  Ni umuyobozi mukuru wa sosiyete ikorera mu gihugu cya Nigeriya, Nailamedia, yashinzwe mu 2017. <ref name="inmesit">https://www.pulse.ng/bi/lifestyle/nadine-ibrahim-nigerian-filmmaker-talks-about-the-essence-of-being-different/nzp71n0</ref> Filime ye ya documentaire ngufi yitwa ''Marked'', yakoranye imyaka ibiri yatewe inkunga no gushyira ikimenyetso cya nyirasenge, yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco rya Aké ryabereye i Lagos muri 2019. Ireba inkovu gakondo, ikwirakwizwa muri Nijeriya ariko nanone ikaba kirazira, ariko, ubwiza bwayo nibyo Ibrahim yashakaga gutsinda. <ref>https://www.dazeddigital.com/body/article/46557/1/scarification-nadine-ibrahim-marked-documentary-film-nigeria-lagos-taboo</ref>

Ibrahim yanditse Tyler Perry, Alfred Hitchcock, Spike Lee and Ang Leee nk'intangarugero.  Iyindi ngaruka ikomeye avuga ni nyina, binyuze mu mirimo ye muri guverinoma yamenye ubukene na ruswa muri Nijeriya.  Yagizwe umwe mu basore bakomeye ba firime bo muri Nigeriya bareba. <ref>https://shadowandact.com/three-young-nigerian-filmmakers-to-watch</ref> Ibrahim yashakanye na Nasir i [[Abuja]] muri 2017. <ref>https://ng.opera.news/ng/en/entertainment/ca5431dadd89220cf93b4b4dac8b7074</ref>

